{"tid":397360,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA18 Pro Club 招人 備戰HKVPL","createTime":"2017-09-12T12:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T03:16:01.000Z","uid":11637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"479600b6e2c0015462673f30a878d271684a9418","tid":397360,"uid":11637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:05:27.000Z","msg":"成員班底各散東西 於18年重新上路<br />\n<br />\n自問對自己有要求既 歡迎黎試腳 前中後龍門都歡迎<br />\n<br />\n遊戲時間為晚上 需要溝通 56K上網會疾機既免<br />\n<br />\n球隊風格 小組短傳 地面滲透 要求隊員作出溝通 補位等<br />\n<br />\n前鋒 雙翼為主 有護波能力 有個人盤球更佳 唔需要左羊右華 我地唔係莫耶斯帶隊 適當時候拉邊帶散人群 需要無球走動 <br />\n<br />\n中場 需要有護波能力 切勿心雄 亂打反擊 視野佳者歡迎試腳 短傳為主<br />\n<br />\n閘 適當位置感 少量overlap 防守為主 切勿亂標波 守位唔追波守 <br />\n<br />\n中堅 兩個字 穩陣 能夠轉守為攻更佳<br />\n<br />\n歡迎留底TG <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有專人聯絡"},{"pid":"36ddc8001d9a5e156a1ba5e5f7fd8970b4397a3c","tid":397360,"uid":16061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:08:47.000Z","msg":"有錢收嫁? 咁撚多要求"},{"pid":"1cc1b0ef10409fd2dea53cbb5a32266443099aee","tid":397360,"uid":46802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:17:19.000Z","msg":"週薪幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77e755589125659fba0e9d158005bed388a1949","tid":397360,"uid":130781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:18:07.000Z","msg":"Cazorla17"},{"pid":"30ffeaf41d7fecfb319da5e555792e0185bf1440","tid":397360,"uid":80122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:34:14.000Z","msg":"tg <br />\nArshavin0812"},{"pid":"46f632c7879203e48b46ebf017966faa65c17894","tid":397360,"uid":12026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"咁多要求有撚用咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪又係瘋狂撞柱，對方 Alpha Go 龍門，自己龍智障 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji